branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series CVS1 is a double acting, single rod, valve mounted cylinder with built-in speed controller. Operation style can be changed to normally retracted or normally extended. Single, double, and 3 position solenoid valves can be installed. There are seven mounting options available for the CVS1 series and bore sizes range from 40mm to 100mm. An auto switch cylinder with the switch installed can also be manufactured.
&lt;/p&gt;

